78
00:06:57.880 --> 00:07:00.960
Good luck.
WHISPERS: Thank you, sir.

79
00:07:03.800 --> 00:07:05.800
See you tomorrow.

80
00:07:08.920 --> 00:07:16.600
Understandably nervous, Willie
is the first NZ recipient of the
Victoria Cross in 64 years.

81
00:07:16.680 --> 00:07:18.760
You've just gotta relax.

82
00:07:19.120 --> 00:07:20.800
You'll get plenty of this.

83
00:07:20.840 --> 00:07:25.920
It's a fairly daunting prospect to
