anonymity

84
00:07:25.960 --> 00:07:29.440
to becoming a public figure
for the rest of your life.

85
00:07:29.480 --> 00:07:32.280
Three, two, one. Three, two, one.

86
00:07:31.720 --> 00:07:33.720
CLICK! CLICK! CLICK!

87
00:07:35.040 --> 00:07:37.040
OK, you can relax.

88
00:07:42.640 --> 00:07:46.880
Willie gets a crash course in
how to be an overnight hero.

89
00:07:46.920 --> 00:07:52.920
Willie's a very humble person by
nature and not prone to saying
too much.

90
00:07:53.160 --> 00:07:56.880
But that doesn't cut the mustard
