91
00:07:56.920 --> 00:08:01.240
Then people wanna know a little bit
about you and they wanna hear your
story.

92
00:08:01.280 --> 00:08:03.280
You're a hero.

93
00:08:04.240 --> 00:08:09.960
Absolutely. Now, you might need to
