94
00:08:10.000 --> 00:08:12.480
and you're gonna hear it a lot.

95
00:08:13.480 --> 00:08:19.960
As of tomorrow, when the first
radio bulletins go out, you are
a NZ celebrity. >

96
00:08:20.440 --> 00:08:27.120
