102
00:08:50.000 --> 00:08:52.520
At midnight, the
call is made to stop.

103
00:08:52.560 --> 00:08:55.400
We might tell them we're
there. 8am tomorrow?

104
00:08:55.440 --> 00:08:59.880
For Willie, a sleepless night lies
ahead, as he knows that tomorrow,

105
00:08:59.920 --> 00:09:05.520
NZ will be delivered the
groundbreaking news - they have a
new hero.

